---
---

<style>
  .glow-wwa-blue {
    width: 1000px; height: 1000px;
    top: -450px; left: -450px;
  }
  .glow-wwa-violet {
    width: 600px; height: 600px;
    bottom: -230px; right: -50px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .glow-wwa-blue {
      width: 460px; height: 460px;
      top: -207px; left: -207px;
    }
    .glow-wwa-violet {
      width: 280px; height: 280px;
      bottom: -157px; right: -23px;
    }
  }
  /* Parallax coverage only on desktop — mobile gets natural fit, no wasted GPU layer */
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .whoweare-img {
      height: 115%;
      will-change: transform;
    }
  }
</style>

<section class="py-28 px-6 bg-[var(--color-bg)] relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute pointer-events-none rounded-full glow-wwa-blue" aria-hidden="true"
       style="filter: blur(120px); background: rgba(79,110,247,0.18);"></div>
  <div class="absolute pointer-events-none rounded-full glow-wwa-violet" aria-hidden="true"
       style="filter: blur(80px); background: rgba(124,58,237,0.14);"></div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center relative z-10">
    <!-- Left: copy + standalone stat blocks -->
    <div>
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[var(--color-accent)] mb-6">· Who We Are</p>
      <h2 class="font-[var(--font-heading)] text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-[var(--color-text)] leading-tight mb-8" data-animate-heading>
        We don't do vanity metrics. We do results.
      </h2>
      <div data-animate-body>
        <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed mb-5">
          Serve Motions was founded on a simple belief: marketing should make businesses money. Not just generate impressions, likes, or reports that sound impressive but mean nothing.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed mb-5">
          Every strategy we build is grounded in your commercial goals. We work as an extension of your team — accountable, proactive, and obsessed with measurable outcomes.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed">
          Trusted by 200+ clients worldwide, with a 98% retention rate and a 5× average ROI delivered.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Standalone stat blocks -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-10 pt-8 border-t border-[var(--color-border)]">
        <div>
          <span
            class="block font-[var(--font-heading)] text-[4.5rem] leading-none font-extrabold"
            style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4F6EF7, #7C3AED); -webkit-background-clip: text; background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;"
            data-counter
            data-target="200"
          >0</span><span
            class="font-[var(--font-heading)] font-extrabold text-[2.5rem] leading-none"
            style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4F6EF7, #7C3AED); -webkit-background-clip: text; background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;"
          >+</span>
          <span class="block text-[0.75rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mt-2">clients worldwide</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span
            class="block font-[var(--font-heading)] text-[4.5rem] leading-none font-extrabold"
            style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4F6EF7, #7C3AED); -webkit-background-clip: text; background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;"
            data-counter
            data-target="98"
          >0</span><span
            class="font-[var(--font-heading)] font-extrabold text-[2.5rem] leading-none"
            style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4F6EF7, #7C3AED); -webkit-background-clip: text; background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;"
          >%</span>
          <span class="block text-[0.75rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mt-2">client retention rate</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span
            class="block font-[var(--font-heading)] text-[4.5rem] leading-none font-extrabold"
            style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4F6EF7, #7C3AED); -webkit-background-clip: text; background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;"
            data-counter
            data-target="5"
          >0</span><span
            class="font-[var(--font-heading)] font-extrabold text-[2.5rem] leading-none"
            style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4F6EF7, #7C3AED); -webkit-background-clip: text; background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;"
          >×</span>
          <span class="block text-[0.75rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mt-2">average ROI delivered</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Right: professional image with clip-path reveal + Ken Burns entrance + scroll parallax -->
    <figure
      class="relative rounded-[var(--radius-xl)] overflow-hidden m-0"
      style="aspect-ratio: 4/3; max-height: 480px;"
      data-animate-clip
    >
      <img
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522071820081-009f0129c71c?w=800&auto=format&q=80"
        alt="Professional team collaborating on digital strategy"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover whoweare-img"
        data-whoweare-img
        loading="lazy"
        decoding="async"
      />
      <!-- Gradient overlay: grounds image in page color at bottom -->
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none"
        style="background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(8,12,20,0.7) 0%, rgba(79,110,247,0.12) 50%, transparent 100%);"
        aria-hidden="true"
      ></div>
      <!-- Frosted-glass badge -->
      <div class="absolute bottom-6 left-6 z-10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl px-4 py-2 bg-white/10 border border-white/20">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-white/90 uppercase tracking-[0.12em]">200+ Brands Scaled</p>
      </div>
    </figure>
  </div>
</section>
